Quentin Tarantino sits down with Roger Avary on @joeroganexperience episode 2240, bringing decades of filmmaking expertise and their iconic "Pulp Fiction" partnership to the table. The duo, who together host "The Video Archives" podcast, break down their craft and shared history in film. Tarantino's portfolio speaks for itselfâ€”"Once Upon a Time in Hollywood" among countless classicsâ€”while Avary's work on "The Rules of Attraction" showcases his distinct directorial vision.
